{"tid":2234767,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教廷促京續約 逾期未覆恐失效","createTime":"2020-10-08T06:32:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T07:23:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"172aeeffd9a3350f55d43fabd158decf2c25f528","tid":2234767,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T06:32:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201008/NTSFNAG45NANJNFY2VPSPPEVHM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201008%2FNTSFNAG45NANJNFY2VPSPPEVHM%2F&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5Eigq9hDTRyGE5nekVWm24Q%3D&h=1f4e3724\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201008%2FNTSFNAG45NANJNFY2VPSPPEVHM%2F&h=b3208152\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201008/NTSFNAG45NANJNFY2VPSPPEVHM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n教廷促京續約 逾期未覆恐失效<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mgbppjxELOyzEso9UNl74pCvO6g=/660x385/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CXJM4VE5YVDPVHPNQMAZY3RX7I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmgbppjxELOyzEso9UNl74pCvO6g%3D%2F660x385%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCXJM4VE5YVDPVHPNQMAZY3RX7I.jpg&h=85244938&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中梵（圖）主教任命臨時性協議的有效期本月22日屆滿，教廷外長加拉格爾（Paul Richard Gallagher）昨日證實，教廷已向北京遞交續約提議，但尚未收到答覆，若協議到期前未收到回音，協議將自動失效。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱教宗有權任命華主教<br />\n<br />\n加拉格爾昨日接受天主教權威媒體《十字架報》（Crux）專訪時坦言，落實協議的過程很艱困，教廷對協議不是完全滿意，不是每件事都按照預期發展，但教廷不像美國國務卿蓬佩奧（Mike Pompeo）所批評的向中國屈膝，教廷在中梵協議取得重大成果，讓教宗方濟各對中國主教任命有最終發言權。<br />\n<br />\n2018年中梵雙方簽署協議，主要是為了解決中國主教任命問題。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n談到中梵協議的困難，加拉格爾表示主要有兩點：。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n至於美國批評中梵協議可能替中國壓制宗教自由與人權之舉背書，加拉格爾表示，他理解外界會有這類質疑，有些大國可以用商業金融或軍事戰略方式來對應中國，但教廷是小國，跟中國沒有外交關係，「沒有別的牌可打」，必須與中國透過互動解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n中央社"},{"pid":"79099d6392b11c36b39d6968556f4e3229622229","tid":2234767,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T06:35:18.000Z","msg":"奶共教宗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97005bd4fe0e2f58fed1c56ee50f8715833cee01","tid":2234767,"uid":158613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T06:36:33.000Z","msg":"撤旦代言人"},{"pid":"5a54e2bffdffe87ee54ceda17feae1fb42076003","tid":2234767,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T07:23:37.000Z","msg":"第三個花地瑪預言：唔使續約，因為&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}